snippet.title: Hearts Like Clockwork: Teaser
snippet.description:
This is a promotional video for my upcoming project "Hearts Like Clockwork"  A vocaloid fan game where you play as Rin Kagamine, Along with her friends Miku, Luka, and Gumi. As their daily lives are about to take a new turn. And it seems like the (week)end is coming.

For updates: 
https://twitter.com/AmayaKayako
https://kayakoamaya.itch.io/hearts-like-clockwork

Bust art by Melonie Moon
https://meloniemoon.com/

Song: Meltdown by Iroha (sasaki)
Music box version by キューマ
https://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/nm9895247
